  <UtilityGetFingerprint/>

  <!-- <div
  v-if="colors !== null"

  <main
  v-if="fingerprint === 'error'"
  :class="[
    'absolute',
    'w-full h-full',
    'bg-gray-200',
    'hidden sm:block',
    'p-5'
  ]">
    <BasicText :size="'md'" :text="'WebGL disabled. Fingerprint could not be generated.'"/>
  </main>


  <main
  v-else
  :class="[
    'w-full h-full',
    'block sm:hidden',
  ]">
  <BasicText :size="'md'" class="hidden" :text="'This website can only be accessed through a desktop device'"/>


    <LayoutMenu />

    <router-view v-slot="{ Component }" class="">
      <component :is="Component" :key="route.path"/>
    </router-view>

  </main>


</template>

<script>

  import $ from 'jquery'

  import { useRoute } from 'vue-router'
  import LayoutMenu from '@/components/layout/LayoutMenu.vue'
  import BasicText from '@/components/basic/BasicText.vue'
  import UtilityGetFingerprint from '@/components/utilities/UtilityGetFingerprint.vue'


  export default {
    components: {
      LayoutMenu,
      UtilityGetFingerprint,
      BasicText
    },
    setup() {
      return {
        route: useRoute()
      };
    },
    watch: {
      fingerprint: {
        immediate: true,
        handler(newVal, oldVal) {
          if (!$.isEmptyObject(newVal)) {
            this.postData()
          }
        },
      },
    },
    computed: {
      fingerprint() {
        return this.$store.state.fingerprint
      },
    },
    methods: {
      postData() {
        const fingerprint = this.fingerprint
        $.ajax({
            contentType: "application/json", // php://input
            //contentType: "application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=UTF-8", // $_POST
            dataType : "json",
            method: "POST",
            processData: false,
            url: "//thumb.kew-halle.de/postFingerprint.php",
            data: JSON.stringify(this.fingerprint)
        })
        .done(function(data) {
            console.log(data);
        })
        .fail(function(data) {
            console.log(data);
        });
      }
    },
    mounted() {}
  }

</script>

<style lang="scss">
  html {
    font-size: 12px;
  }
  #app {
    @apply h-full;
  }
  body {
    @apply absolute;
    @apply h-full;
    @apply w-full;
    @apply bg-gray-300;
  }

  @media print {

     html {
       -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
     }

     @page {
       size: 240mm 310mm;
       padding: 0;
       margin: 0mm;
    }

    .layout-nav {
      display: none;
    }
  }

</style>
